    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2018 executive sedan that perfectly balances luxury with everyday practicality. The exterior showcases a deep metallic finish that still catches the light beautifully, with only minor road-pebble chips on the lower valance consistent with light highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the charcoal leather seats are supple and free of cracks, and the genuine wood trim retains its original luster. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been strictly maintained with synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts with seamless precision. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with plenty of life left, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This is a non-smoker, pet-free vehicle that has spent most of its life in a climate-controlled garage, offering the next owner a reliable and sophisticated driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
